        "subject": "LU-13498 tests: reproduce sanity 56w failure",
        "message": "LU-13498 tests: reproduce sanity 56w failure\n\nA patch recently landed to master that is making sanity\ntest 56w fail at a high rate.  Run the test several times\nto capture the failure rate and this can inform the number\nof times to run any solutions/revert of landed patches.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nTest-Parameters: env=SHARED_KEY=true,ONLY=\"55-56\" austeroptions=-H mdscount=2 mdtcount=4 testlist=sanity\nTest-Parameters: env=SHARED_KEY=true,ONLY=\"50-56\" austeroptions=-H mdscount=2 mdtcount=4 testlist=sanity\n\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <jnunez@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ia6b4e4602f8c09326388c2cd047a21c81ac3de8f\n"
      },
